# MCP Manager CLI

A unified CLI and daemon/service to manage and proxy multiple MCP servers, with robust logging and a modern CLI UX.

**âš¡ Powered by [CloudThinker](https://www.cloudthinker.io/) - The Future of Cloud Operations**

